scaling is easy
payment is based on usage

This is similar to cloud computing.

The cloud provider manages infrastructure while customers focus on applications and business requirements.

Why Cloud Computing Became Necessary

Modern applications require:

global accessibility
high scalability
continuous availability
rapid deployments
automatic scaling
secure communication

Traditional infrastructure struggles to handle these efficiently.

Cloud computing solves these problems using:

virtualization
